## General

This is production mobile cross-platform (Expo - React Native - Ignite boilerplate) application, for home owners, that communicates with our backend (betterplace_api_django) that is available at our workspace.

## Goal

We are aiming to create clean internationalized production application

## Solution planning

Always include neat UI animations where appropriate into solution planning
If you need to use any plain text string - you should use it from the translation, if it not there probably should create one

